our lease purchase program is straight forward and one of the most successful out there . you pay off the truck you get the title . at sammons the only way we succeed is if you succeed . we have the resources to support you , as long as you have the determination . we do not require a down payment or any up_front costs to get into our lease purchase program . we do require our contractors run rand mcnally electronic logs . we take great pride in the slogan safety_first . we adhere to the following guidelines in our hiring practices . if you have any questions on qualifications , please_contact a recruiter in the missoula office at 1-855-233-9004 . applicants need to have at least 12 months of open deck experience ( flat , step or rgn ) . we also require at least 24 months of added to the truck earnings . to figure your truck payment we take the total truck earnings ( line_haul + fuel surcharge ) and subtract the operating expenses . typical operating expenses include , fuel , maintenance , insurance , trailer rental , etc . our weekly trailer rental includes tires , maintenance , licensing and insurance . we have a contractor services department that is here to help
